 * Discover, profile and catalog folder-type data sources via the MCP
 * DataDiscoveryAgent.
 *
 * API calls (all via MCP orchestration):
 *   POST /api/agentic/discovery   ΓåÆ discover + profile a folder source
 *   GET  /api/data-sources        ΓåÆ list registered datasources
 *   POST /api/agentic/quality-scan ΓåÆ run DQ scan on a discovered source
 */

